senior creative writing portfolios home award winners levinthals fiction poetry non fiction archive info creative writing program questions killeenh stanford edu bldg 460 creative writing is so often a personal experience what is produced is often kept private or shared with only a select handful a teacher perhaps or a critique group this gallery and archive of creative writing at stanford university is a forum for undergraduate senior poets and fiction and nonfiction writers to showcase an example of their creative work we hope this site will not only serve as an archive of the best that the stanford undergraduate creative writing program has produced over the years but that it will also encourage future students to produce writing that they are proud to claim please do peruse our growing gallery for inspiration and motivation from these emerging young writers submit your own work
